OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving during chase
OL,6,FA police officer accused of killing a
OL,7,Fwoman by driving dangerously during a
OL,8,Fcar chase will go on trial in January
OL,9,F2026.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police Constable
OL,12,FMatthew Pike was driving an unmarked
OL,13,Fpolice car involved in a pursuit
OL,14,Fthrough Bristol city centre in
OL,15,FNovember 2021.
OL,17,FThe car he was pursuing - a Volkswagen
OL,18,FTiguan - was involved in a fatal
OL,19,Fcollision with a Honda Jazz in
OL,20,FNewfoundland Circus.
