OL,3,CPolice officer accused of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving during chase
OL,6,FDoctor Keryl Johnson was driving the
OL,7,FHonda. The 35-year-old was taken to
OL,8,Fhospital with life-threatening
OL,9,Finjuries and died there 11 days later.
OL,11,FPike, who is 38 years old, is charged
OL,12,Fwith one count of causing death by
OL,13,Fdangerous driving and is due to go on
OL,14,Ftrial on 5 January, 2026.
OL,16,FThe police officer also faces an
OL,17,Falternative charge of causing death by
OL,18,Fcareless or inconsiderate driving,
OL,19,Frelating to the same alleged victim.
