OL,3,CPolice officer accused of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving during chase
OL,6,FThe charges allege Pike was driving a
OL,7,FBMW on roads including Temple Gate,
OL,8,FTemple Way, Bond Street, the Bearpit
OL,9,Froundabout, King's Square Avenue,
OL,10,FArmada Place, Nine Tree Hill and
OL,11,FBrigstocke Road.
OL,13,FPike, who sat in the dock during the
OL,14,Fshort hearing, spoke to confirm his
OL,15,Fname and to confirm he could hear
OL,16,Fproceedings.
OL,18,FThe officer did not enter pleas to the
OL,19,Fcharges against him.
