OL,3,CPolice officer accused of causing
OL,4,Cdeath by dangerous driving during chase
OL,6,FJudge Peter Blair KC, the Recorder of
OL,7,FBristol, released Pike on
OL,8,Funconditional bail.
OL,10,FJocelyn Ledward KC, prosecuting, told
OL,11,Fthe court: "This case arises out of a
OL,12,Ffatal collision that took place very
OL,13,Fshortly after midnight on 5 November
OL,14,F2021 which resulted in the death of
OL,15,FKeryl Johnson."
OL,17,FMs Ledward said the trial is estimated
OL,18,Fto last between 10 and 15 days.
OL,20,FRamin Pakrooh represented Pike during
OL,21,Fthe hearing.
