OL,6,FIn a statement, the Independent Office
OL,7,Ffor Police Conduct previously said:
OL,8,F"The officer was driving an unmarked
OL,9,Fpolice vehicle and was pursuing a
OL,10,FVolkswagen Tiguan which had failed to
OL,11,Fstop for police.
OL,13,F"During the pursuit the Volkswagen
OL,14,FTiguan collided with a Honda Jazz.
OL,16,F"The driver of the Honda sadly died in
OL,17,Fhospital after sustaining serious
OL,18,Finjuries in the collision."
